.DT
set_how_many
Disk World creator help
set_how_many

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_how_many -  This method sets how many doors there are so that plurals and everything are set correctly.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_how_many(int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the number of doors this door should represent.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/door.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets how many doors there are so that plurals
and everything are set correctly.  It also flags the door
with the "group object" property.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_how_many()

.EP

